date: Sun Feb 13 2022 15:06:51 GMT+1100 (Australian Eastern Daylight Time)
description: Casey O'Neill beat Roxanne Modafferi in a split-decision at UFC 271 in Houston. The Aussie flyweight set a new record for significant strikes in a three-round fight at 125 pounds. The win improves her UFC record to 4-0 (9-0) as a professional. Questions have been raised over the scoring of the fight.
metaDescription: This image of  Aussie flyweight Casey O'Neill was created by an AI after she beat Roxanne Modafferi in a split-decision at UFC 271 in Houston
